stories.title: Urdu Report - Sharjah Cup 5th Match: New Zealand v Sri Lanka
Lankans sail into the Sharjah Cup final
stories.summary: SHARJAH--Sri Lanka notched another win, their third out of four in this event, to be the first to make it to the final of this Sharjah Cup 2002, leaving Pakistan and New Zealand to slug it out for the other berth today

stories.title: Urdu Report - Sharjah Cup 5th Match: New Zealand v Sri Lanka
Lankans sail into the Sharjah Cup final
stories.summary: SHARJAH--Sri Lanka notched another win, their third out of four in this event, to be the first to make it to the final of this Sharjah Cup 2002, leaving Pakistan and New Zealand to slug it out for the other berth today
